titles.title: A bill to provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain entries of dog and cat treats as free of certain duties.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 1/21/1993--Introduced. Directs the Secretary of the Treasury to liquidate or reliquidate as duty-free, and provide for the refund of duties on, certain entries of dog and cat treats in the Chicago, Illinois, Customs District.
